This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for improving accuracy in lexical multiple choice problems. The paper specifically focuses on ensemble methods for combining the output of multiple modules. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
